New Orleans Louisiana in the early 90’s was deemed the Murder Capital of the World, certain areas and neighborhoods even today are off limits for travelers , locals and even people from the area. The #MagnoliaProject is among the largest and notorious, housing approximately 2,100 people. It is also home to numerous hip-hop artists and is located in the part of uptown New Orleans known as Central City. @magnolialevee takes us on ride through #Uptown and tells us some untold stories of his late friend, Hip Hop Legend #SouljaSlim , Going to school with #Lilwayne , Do’s and Dont’s in the hood and more🔥🔥
